Hydro Quebec is issuing a 125 mlnCanadian dlr bond due April 21, 1997 paying nine pct and pricedat 100-3/4 pct, lead manager Merrill Lynch International said.    The bond is available in denominations of 1,000 and 5,000dlrs and will be listed in Luxembourg.    Fees comprise 1-1/4 pct selling concession and 3/8 pct eachfor management and underwriting. Pay date is April 21. REUTER&#3;